---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import { getImage } from 'astro:assets';
import slide1 from './../images/slide1.webp';
import slide2 from '../images/slide2.webp';
import slide3 from '../images/slide3.webp';
import slide4 from '../images/slide4.webp';
import slide5 from '../images/slide5.webp';
import imageWorks from '../images/3.webp';
import business from '../images/business-standard.webp';
import forbes from '../images/forbes-india.webp';
import cnbc from '../images/cnbc.webp';
import health from '../images/health-world.webp';
import inc from '../images/inc-42-footer-logo-1.webp';
import live from '../images/live-mint.webp';
import netmed from '../images/1.webp';
import tata from '../images/3-1.webp';
import untitled from '../images/untitled-design-1.webp';
const optimizedBackground = await getImage({src: imageWorks, format: 'webp'});

---

<Layout>
  <section class="hero bg-cover bg-center " style={`background-image: url(${optimizedBackground.src});`}>
	<div class="h-screen flex items-center justify-center  bg-black/70">
		<div class="text-center w-[66%]" style="min-width: 50%;">
			<h1 class="text-7xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-8 px-10 ">Experience Relief with Coroquil-Zn</h1>
			<p class="text-2xl text-white px-10 mb-8">Boost Your Immunity with Our Innovative Zinc-Based Formula</p>
			<div class="text-center">
				<a href="/Discover" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center text-[#645600] bg-[#fff197] rounded-full p-4 text-2xl font-bold hover: cursor-pointer hover:bg-[#f9e356]">Discover COROQUIL-Zn</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
  </section>
  <section class="bg-[#2e481a] flex flex-col items-center justify-center pt-10 mb-10">
	<div class="ml-10 mr-10 flex flex-col items-center justify-center pb-10" style="max-width: 800px;">
		<h1 class="text-7xl text-white text-center p-7">Introducing <strong>COROQUIL-Zn</strong></h1>
		<p class="text-2xl text-white text-center pb-7">
			At Remedium, we are dedicated to developing innovative health solutions that improve your quality of life. Our latest product, COROQUIL-Zn, is designed to enhance your immune system and provide reliable support for your overall wellness. With a unique blend of zinc and other natural ingredients, COROQUIL-Zn offers an effective approach to maintaining a healthy immune response and promoting overall health.
		</p>
		<p class="text-2xl text-white text-center pb-7">
			Recently approved by the Ayush Administration for use in mild to moderate COVID-19 and other respiratory ailments, COROQUIL-Zn is designed to enhance your immune system and overall wellness.
		</p>
	</div>
  </section>
  <!-- Slideshow -->
  <section class="bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center ">
	<div class="relative w-full max-w-3xl m-auto overflow-hidden">
	  <!-- Slideshow Container -->
	  <div class="slideshow-container relative w-full h-120">
		<!-- Slide Images -->
		<div class="mySlides fade hidden">
		  <Image src={slide1} alt="A description of pruduct1." class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
		</div>
		<div class="mySlides fade hidden">
		  <Image src={slide2} alt="A description of product2." class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
		</div>
		<div class="mySlides fade hidden">
		  <Image src={slide3} alt="A description of product3." class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
		</div>
		<div class="mySlides fade hidden">
		  <Image src={slide4} alt="A description of  product4." class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
		</div>
		<div class="mySlides fade hidden">
		  <Image src={slide5} alt="A description of product5." class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
		</div>
	  </div>
	
	  <!-- Navigation Buttons -->
	  <a class="prev absolute left-0 top-1/2 transform -translate-y-1/2 text-2xl text-white cursor-pointer">❮</a>
	  <a class="next absolute right-0 top-1/2 transform -translate-y-1/2 text-2xl text-white cursor-pointer">❯</a>
	</div>
  
	<!-- Add Slideshow Script -->
	<script>
	  let slideIndex = 0;
	  showSlides();
  
	  function showSlides() {
		const slides = document.querySelectorAll('.mySlides');
		slides.forEach(slide => slide.classList.add('hidden'));
		slideIndex++;
		if (slideIndex > slides.length) slideIndex = 1;
		slides[slideIndex - 1].classList.remove('hidden');
		setTimeout(showSlides, 4000); // Change image every 4 seconds
	  }
	</script>
  </section>
  <section class="pt-10 pb-10 flex justify-center">
  	<div class="bg-[#393193] rounded-3xl" style="max-width: 85%;">
		<div class="m-5 pt-8 pb-8 flex flex-col text-left">
			<h1 class="text-[#FFD7EF] text-7xl font-bold">What is COROQUIL-Zn?</h1>
			<p class="pt-4 text-[#FFD7EF] text-2xl">
				COROQUIL-Zn is a cutting-edge zinc-based supplement developed by Remedium to support your immune health. Our product combines the benefits of zinc with a proprietary blend of natural ingredients to help your body fend off illnesses and maintain optimal health. Zinc is an essential mineral known for its immune-boosting properties, and in COROQUIL-Zn, we've harnessed its power to deliver maximum effectiveness. 
			</p>
			<p class="pt-4 text-[#FFD7EF] text-2xl">
				Crafted with high-quality, natural components, COROQUIL-Zn is designed to be a safe, effective, and easy addition to your daily wellness routine. Each ingredient is carefully selected to provide comprehensive immune support and help you stay healthy and vibrant.
			</p>
			<p class="pt-4 text-[#FFD7EF] text-2xl">
				Crafted with high-quality, natural components, COROQUIL-Zn is designed to be a safe, effective, and easy addition to your daily wellness routine. By taking two capsules a day, you can maintain strong immune support and promote overall health. Each ingredient is carefully selected to provide comprehensive immune support and help you stay healthy and vibrant.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
  </section>
  <section class="bg-[#2E481A] flex flex-col items-center justify-center w-[100%] pt-20 pb-20 mb-20">
		<div class="bg-[#9FE870] w-[90%] rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center p-12 " style="max-width: 80%;">
			<p class="text-[#2E481A] text-6xl font-bold text-center m-15">
				Approved by Ministry of Ayush, Govt. of India for adjuvant treatment of COVID-19 
