		</div>
  </section>

  <section class=" ">
	<div class="text-center mb-10">
		<h1 class="text-6xl pb-5"><strong>How COROQUIL-Zn Works</strong></h1>
		<p class="text-2xl">
			COROQUIL-Zn works by leveraging the power of zinc and other natural ingredients to support and strengthen your immune system. Here's how our formula helps: 
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="inline-flex flex-row justify-center flex-nowrap">
